      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>chopped potatoes</strong> and <strong>creamy vegetable stock</strong> and cook for 15-18 min or until the potatoes are almost fork-tender</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
