    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the potatoes are almost fork-tender, add the <strong>chopped smoked basa</strong>, <strong>soft cheese</strong> and <strong>drained</strong> <strong>sweetcorn </strong>to the pan and gently stir it all together</p><p>Cook for 4-5 min or until the<strong> </strong>smoked basa is cooked through and the potatoes are fork-tender – this is your <strong>one-pot</strong> <strong>smoked basa, leek & sweetcorn chowder</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked when it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
